    "The first transformative GenAI capability, from which GenAI derives its name, is at the very core of this technology-the ability to generate (i.e., create) new content.",
    "Although the concept and pursuit of machine creativity is not new (e.g., Boden, 1998), the increasing uptake and evolution of GenAI raises new possibilities and questions with regard to: (1) the characteristics and features of machine creativity, (2) the measurement of machine creativity, and (3) machine creativity techniques.",
